  "general_provisions": "This bill modifies provisions related to charter school authorization and funding.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>establishes a uniform funding mechanism for charter school authorizers (authorizers);<hr><ltbullet>creates startup funding for a new authorizer;<hr><ltbullet>modifies provisions for the State Charter School Board;<hr><ltbullet>creates procedures for charter schools to transfer between authorizers;<hr><ltbullet>reallocates administrative funding;<hr><ltbullet>adds fee payment compliance to charter school requirements;<hr><ltbullet>modifies asset distribution priorities in school closures;<hr><ltbullet>includes authorizer fees in grounds for termination; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical changes.",
